from gomer richard j coyle subject re how difficult be it to get penguin ticket in article dmoney dean r money write the subject line say it all is it terribly difficult to get ticket to penguin game especially now that they be in the playoff would it be easy to find scalper outside of the igloo sell ticket there be alway scalper with ticket outside the arena you might have to pay a few buck extra but you can alway find them look on the street under the message board or out on the street in front of the hyatt or even around gate the later you buy them the le money you pay and during the regular season you could usually find some for near face value or below if you wait until game time might be better to pick them up earlier now though rick 